                          the positions of Administrative Assistant and Driver for various places.
                          Job hunters who are interested and eligible for the positions can apply on or 
                          before 7th April, 2015. Find more details about the positions given below.

<b>Total No. of Positions :</b> Not Specified 

<b>Name of Positions :</b> Administrative Assistant and Driver
 <b>Last Date:</b> 27-June-2015<hr /> 

